gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Hi! Sorry to keep you waiting!\p"
	.string "Welcome to Emerald Hope!\p"
	.string "My name is Birch, the\n"
	.string "Pokémon Professor.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "This is what we call a “Pokémon.”\p"
	.string "\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
	.string "This world is widely inhabited by\n"
	.string "creatures known as Pokémon.\p"
	.string "We humans live alongside Pokémon,\n"
	.string "at times as friendly playmates, and\l"
	.string "at times as cooperative workmates.\p"
	.string "And sometimes, we band together\n"
	.string "and battle others like us.\p"
	.string "But despite our closeness, we don't\n"
	.string "know everything about Pokémon.\p"
	.string "In fact, there are many, many\n"
	.string "secrets surrounding Pokémon.\p"
	.string "To unravel Pokémon mysteries,\n"
	.string "I've been undertaking research.\l"
	.string "That's what I do.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
	.string "That's enough about me though.\p"
	.string "Tell me about yourself!$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
	.string "How do you prefer to look?\n"
	.string "Option 1 or 2?$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
	.string "All right.\n"
	.string "What's your name?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
	.string "So it's {PLAYER}{KUN}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "Ah, okay!\p"
	.string "You're {PLAYER}{KUN} who's moving to my\n"
	.string "hometown of Littleroot.\l"
	.string "I get it now!\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "All right, are you ready?\p"
	.string "Your very own adventure is about\n"
	.string "to unfold.\p"
	.string "Take courage, and leap into the\n"
	.string "world of Pokémon where dreams,\l"
	.string "adventure, and friendships await!\p"
	.string "Well, I'll be expecting you later.\n"
	.string "Come see me in my Pokémon Lab.\p"
	.string "...\p"
	.string "... hi!\n"
	.string "this is maddie, creator of emerald hope!\p"
	.string "you're currently playing a DEMO VERSION\n"
	.string "which ends just outside of slateport.\p"
	.string "the full release will come in 2024,\n"
	.string "and cover the entire game of emerald!\p"
	.string "this will be the ONLY demo release, to\n"
	.string "introduce the game and its concepts to\l"
	.string "the romhacking community.\p"
	.string "hope is ostensibly a difficulty hack,\n"
	.string "although it reaches beyond that.\p"
	.string "more specificially, to create a fresh\n"
	.string "and engaging playthrough experience,\l"
	.string "AND a healthy metagame for all kinds\l"
	.string "of competitive gameplay.\p"
	.string "the game is fully playable, and it\n"
	.string "includes thorough changes to gameplay\l"
	.string "as well as extensive QoL features.\p"
	.string "the heart of the hack is a testing\n"
	.string "ground and source of experience for\l"
	.string "a much more ambitious hack to come.\p"
	.string "i've made sure that tutorials and info\n"
	.string "for all the mechanical changes in the\l"
	.string "hack are contained in-game, so DONT\l"
	.string "mash through text, and read everything!\p"
	.string "however, if you want complete details\n"
	.string "on everything changed, please refer\l"
	.string "to the provided documentation.\p"
	.string "have fun, experiment thoroughly,\n"
	.string "and most importantly, trans rights!\p"
	.string "$"
